# Test Compatibility Package

This is a minimal test package used for integration testing of the PHP Compatibility Tester.

## Purpose

This package provides a simple, framework-agnostic test case that can be installed in various PHP frameworks to verify that the compatibility tester works correctly.

## Structure

- `src/TestService.php` - Simple service class
- `composer.json` - Package configuration

## Usage

This package is used internally by the compatibility tester's integration tests. It should not be published or used in production.
